        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500">
            Rio Tinto Bets Big on Lithium
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Rio Tinto is making a <a href="https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/investing/2024/10/11/rio-takes-step-toward-ma-redemption-with-67-billion-lithium-bet/" target="_blank">$6.7 billion</a> bet on lithium with its acquisition of Arcadium Lithium. After past M&A missteps, the miner is looking to position itself as a key player in the booming battery market. The deal could make Rio the third-largest lithium producer by 2030. While investors are cautiously optimistic, some remain wary of Rio’s return to large acquisitions. However, CEO Jakob Stausholm’s disciplined approach seems to have won some over, as Rio strategically moves into greener metals to secure its future.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider
          border-width="1px"
          border-style="solid"
          border-color="lightgrey"
          padding="10px 12px"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
